            "information": "*English:*\r\n\r\nThis competition will hold **only 3x3x3 Fewest Moves event**, and it will be held in multiple locations, across Latin America. Please pay attention to the **date and time zone** of your [location](https:\/\/www.worldcubeassociation.org\/competitions\/FMCLatinAmerica2023#24247-locations-lugares)!\r\n\r\nLocations may be added until the 25th of February 23:59UTC so if there isn't a location near you yet contact your local [Delegate](https:\/\/www.worldcubeassociation.org\/delegates) in Latin America.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n*Espa\u00f1ol:*\r\n\r\nEsta competencia tendr\u00e1 **solo el evento 3x3x3 Menos Movimientos**, y se llevar\u00e1 a cabo en m\u00faltiples ubicaciones en Am\u00e9rica Latina. \u00a1Preste atenci\u00f3n a la **fecha y zona horaria** de su [ubicaci\u00f3n](https:\/\/www.worldcubeassociation.org\/competitions\/FMCLatinAmerica2023#24247-locations-lugares)!\r\n\r\nSe pueden agregar ubicaciones hasta el 25 de febrero a las 23:59 UTC, por lo que si a\u00fan no hay una ubicaci\u00f3n cerca de usted, comun\u00edquese con su [Delegado](https:\/\/www.worldcubeassociation.org\/delegates) local en Am\u00e9rica Latina.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n*Portugu\u00eas:*\r\n\r\nEsta competi\u00e7\u00e3o contar\u00e1 **apenas com a modalidade 3x3x3 Menos Movimentos** e ser\u00e1 realizada em v\u00e1rios locais da Am\u00e9rica Latina. Preste aten\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e0 **data e fuso hor\u00e1rio** da sua [localidade](https:\/\/www.worldcubeassociation.org\/competitions\/FMCLatinAmerica2023#24247-locations-lugares)!\r\n\r\nOs locais podem ser adicionados at\u00e9 25 de fevereiro \u00e0s 23h59 UTC, portanto, se ainda n\u00e3o houver um local pr\u00f3ximo a voc\u00ea, entre em contato com o [Delegado](https:\/\/www.worldcubeassociation.org\/delegates) local na Am\u00e9rica Latina.",
